      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's a number that should stop you in your tracks: WhatsApp messages have a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "98% open rate",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". Compare that to email's average of 20-25%. That's not a marginal improvement—that's a completely different conversation with your audience.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "People check WhatsApp like they check their pulse. It's personal, it's immediate, and it's where trust is built fast. Businesses that recognize this are already outpacing competitors who are still fighting for inbox placement.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The problem? Managing WhatsApp conversations at scale without automation is chaos. That's where Wati comes in. It gives you the official API (no risk of bans), plus a toolkit that turns those conversations into revenue.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
