          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Wati isn't trying to be everything to everyone. It focuses on WhatsApp, and it does that exceptionally well. Here's what sets it apart:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Official WhatsApp Business API Access",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Getting approved for WhatsApp's API on your own can take weeks and involve confusing verification steps. Wati streamlines the entire process. You sign up, connect your number, and they handle the Meta verification. I had mine running in under 48 hours.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No-Code Chatbot Builder",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You don't need a developer to build chatbots with Wati. Their drag-and-drop flow builder lets you create automated responses, qualification sequences, and even order flows without writing a single line of code. I built a complete lead qualification bot in about 30 minutes—something that would have taken a developer a full day.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Broadcast Messaging",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Need to announce a flash sale to 5,000 contacts? Wati's broadcast feature lets you send bulk messages that feel personal. You can segment by tags, past interactions, or custom fields. The delivery rates are phenomenal because, again, it's the official API—no sketchy workarounds.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Built-In CRM",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Wati includes a shared team inbox with basic CRM functionality. Every conversation is logged, searchable, and assignable. For a team of 2-10 people handling customer support and sales, this is more than enough. No need to pay for a separate CRM and then figure out how to connect it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Integrations That Actually Work",
