        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Wati connects natively with Shopify, WooCommerce, HubSpot, Google Sheets, and Zapier (which opens the door to thousands more apps). I linked it to a client's Shopify store in 15 minutes, and order confirmations started going out automatically via WhatsApp. Customers loved it.",
