      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Wati now includes AI-driven suggested responses in the team inbox. When a customer asks a common question, the system pre-fills a relevant answer based on your knowledge base. Agents can approve, tweak, or send it as-is. Response times dropped by 40% in my tests.",
