      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Running Facebook or Instagram ads? Wati lets you connect Click-to-WhatsApp ads directly to your chatbot flows. Someone taps your ad, lands in a WhatsApp conversation, and the bot takes over with a pre-built welcome sequence. The lead quality from this setup was noticeably higher than standard lead form ads.",
