      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Instead of asking customers to type responses, you can now send messages with up to 3 clickable buttons or a list of up to 10 options. This dramatically reduces friction. I used it for a restaurant client's ordering flow, and completion rates jumped from 55% to 82%.",
