            "text": "Connect Wati to your Shopify or WooCommerce store. When someone abandons a cart, wait 30 minutes, then send a friendly WhatsApp message with a direct link back to their cart. Add a small discount code if they don't return in 24 hours. Recovery rates of 25-35% are realistic—I've seen it firsthand.",
