      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Service businesses (salons, clinics, consultants) can use Wati's chatbot to let customers book appointments directly in WhatsApp. Pair it with automated reminders 24 hours and 1 hour before the appointment. No-shows plummet.",
