        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Build a chatbot that asks 3-5 qualifying questions. Based on the answers, tag the lead and route it to the right sales rep—or disqualify it automatically. One e-commerce client went from manually qualifying 200 leads/day to letting the bot handle 80% of them.",
            "marks": []
