        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Set up a bot that handles FAQs (shipping times, return policy, order status) automatically. When a question gets too complex, the bot escalates to a human agent with the full conversation context. Customers feel heard; your team focuses on real problems.",
            "marks": []
          }
