      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Wati offers tiered pricing starting with a Growth plan suitable for small businesses. Plans scale based on the number of contacts and features you need. They also charge per-conversation fees as set by Meta for Business-initiated messages. You can check current pricing on their website and start with a free trial to test the platform before committing.",
